channel.title: Please Reply Soon. (.py file help)
channel.description:
Okay guys, I know someone here has their smarty pants on!
My issue: My server, Project Insanity base, is run off of .py files for objects, and such. My computer does not read these for some reason? So I changed it so my computer would read it with adobe, this still did not work. I need help please!(:
Without it I cannot change shops or add objects anywhere. I kinda' need this? -Sammy
Okay so never mind, I am leaving this up for future reference to anyone that has this dumb issue. JUST DOWNLOAD NOTEPAD++
